title: Tyga Interview and More
itunes:title: Tyga Interview and More
description:
Thursday 7/20 – Today on the show Tyga came by and we went straight to the tea and asked “How did you let Kylie Jenner go?” Tyga also let us in about the Kardashian clan, Blac Chyna and more. Charlamagne gave “Donkey of the Day” to a man that called 911 for stolen cocaine and Angela helped some listeners out with Ask Yee, with one being absolutely fine being a side piece.
